I just have to take a moment and recognize the wonderful staff at this location. After experiencing a horrible experience with Uber eats this five guys location made sure I got my complete order and cooked everything fresh. I used Uber Eats for the first time and half of my order was missing. Not to mention the driver kept the food. I called Uber eats and all they wanted to do was credit me for the items I was missing. The food was cold and I don't know what all the driver touched in my order so I was not eating it nor were my coworkers. I called the Five guys location not thinking there was much they could do and Annette(I believe that is how it is spelled) said that if I could get to the location they would make the burgers for me and fries. After getting to them she had everything made fresh and even made the milkshakes over. Every single worker there was sympathetic and took great care of us! I will definitely go back when I am in the area! As for Uber eats? That was my first and my last time using them.
